SUMMARY TABLE
━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

── v4 BOUNDED ELASTIC CONTINUUM (BEC) ──────────────────────────────────
Parameter              Default  Type    Notes
─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
a_eq_bec               0.0      float   ACTIVATES v4; BEC equilibrium scale factor
P_max_bec              0.0      float   ACTIVATES v4; max restoring pressure [Mpc^-2]
k_bec                  1.0      float   Saturation rate constant
n_bec                  1.0      float   Pressure onset power-law exponent
Gamma_min_bec          0.0      float   Dilation floor (set > 0 when alpha_bec or m_bec > 0)
alpha_bec              0.0      float   Dilation-density coupling via (a/a_eq)^alpha
m_bec                  1.0      float   Stiffening exponent via a^m in Gamma_pow
